title: Killers Amongst Us: Florida's missing Jennifer Kesse showered and dressed for work, then vanished (part 3)
itunes:title: Killers Amongst Us: Florida's missing Jennifer Kesse showered and dressed for work, then vanished (part 3)
description:
As the search continues for Jennifer Kesse, her black Malibu is found in an apartment complex about a mile away. What evidence can be found? And what about the construction going on in Jennifer's apartment complex? Jennifer's parents, Drew Joyce Kesse, tell us more about the evidence found in their daughter's car and what police have done with it... very little according to them.
